<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DVNC.ai - Leonardo's Digital Intelligence</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-gold: #D4A574;
            --secondary-gold: #F5E6D3;
            --deep-charcoal: #1a1a1a;
            --soft-gray: #f5f5f7;
            --text-primary: #2c3e50;
            --text-secondary: #6c757d;
            --accent-blue: #3498db;
            --nature-green: #27ae60;
            --physics-blue: #2980b9;
            --art-purple: #9b59b6;
            --engineering-orange: #f39c12;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display", "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fafafa 0%, #f0f0f0 100%);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Vitruvian Man watermark */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 200 200" opacity="0.03"><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="90" fill="none" stroke="%23D4A574" stroke-width="0.5"/><rect x="55" y="55" width="90" height="90" fill="none" stroke="%23D4A574" stroke-width="0.5"/></svg>') center/contain no-repeat;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2);
            padding: 20px 30px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 10;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-gold), var(--secondary-gold));
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: var(--deep-charcoal);
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        /* Intelligence Indicators */
        .intelligence-status {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .domain-indicator {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .domain-indicator.art { background: var(--art-purple); animation-delay: 0s; }
        .domain-indicator.engineering { background: var(--engineering-orange); animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        .domain-indicator.biology { background: var(--nature-green); animation-delay: 1s; }
        .domain-indicator.physics { background: var(--physics-blue); animation-delay: 1.5s; }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.3); }
        }

        /* Main Chat Container */
        .chat-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Messages Area */
        .messages-area {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        .messages-area::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }

        .messages-area::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: transparent;
        }

        .messages-area::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        /* Message Styles */
        .message {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.4s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(10px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .message.user {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .message-content {
            max-width: 70%;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .message.user .message-content {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-blue), #2980b9);
            color: white;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
        }

        .message.assistant .message-content {
            background: white;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .message-meta {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .thinking-indicator {
            display: inline-flex;
            gap: 4px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .thinking-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary-gold);
            animation: thinking 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .thinking-dot:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .thinking-dot:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

        @keyframes thinking {
            0%, 60%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 0.4;
            }
            30% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        /* Input Area */
        .input-area {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 -10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2);
            margin: 0 20px 20px;
        }

        .input-field {
            flex: 1;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            font-size: 15px;
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .input-field::placeholder {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* Buttons */
        .btn-send {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-gold), #C49660);
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-send:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-send:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .btn-send svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }

        /* Mode Selector */
        .mode-selector {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 4px;
            background: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.8);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .mode-btn {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .mode-btn.active {
            background: white;
            color: var(--deep-charcoal);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Welcome Screen */
        .welcome-screen {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .welcome-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 200;
            color: var(--deep-charcoal);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .welcome-subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .suggestion-cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .suggestion-card {
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .suggestion-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-color: var(--primary-gold);
        }

        .suggestion-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .suggestion-card:nth-child(1) .suggestion-icon { background: rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.1); color: var(--art-purple); }
        .suggestion-card:nth-child(2) .suggestion-icon { background: rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.1); color: var(--engineering-orange); }
        .suggestion-card:nth-child(3) .suggestion-icon { background: rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.1); color: var(--nature-green); }
        .suggestion-card:nth-child(4) .suggestion-icon { background: rgba(41, 128, 185, 0.1); color: var(--physics-blue); }

        .suggestion-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header {
                padding: 16px 20px;
            }
            
            .logo-text {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .message-content {
                max-width: 85%;
            }
            
            .suggestion-cards {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
        <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo-icon">DV</div>
            <div>
                <div class="logo-text">DVNC.ai</div>
                <div class="tagline">Leonardo's Intelligence Reimagined</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mode-selector">
            <button class="mode-btn active">Explore</button>
            <button class="mode-btn">Design</button>
            <button class="mode-btn">Innovate</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="intelligence-status">
            <div class="domain-indicator art" title="Art & Aesthetics"></div>
            <div class="domain-indicator engineering" title="Engineering"></div>
            <div class="domain-indicator biology" title="Biology & Nature"></div>
            <div class="domain-indicator physics" title="Physics & Mathematics"></div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Chat Container -->
    <div class="chat-container">
        <div class="messages-area" id="messagesArea">
            <!-- Welcome Screen -->
            <div class="welcome-screen" id="welcomeScreen">
                <h1 class="welcome-title">Think Like Leonardo</h1>
                <p class="welcome-subtitle">
                    I blend art, science, engineering, and nature to help you see your challenges through Leonardo's interdisciplinary lens. 
                    What complex problem shall we explore together?
                </p>
                
                <div class="suggestion-cards">
                    <div class="suggestion-card" onclick="sendSuggestion('How can biomimicry inspire a more efficient cooling system?')">
                        <div class="suggestion-icon">🍃</div>
                        <div class="suggestion-text">Explore biomimicry in product design</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="suggestion-card" onclick="sendSuggestion('Design a bridge that is both structurally sound and aesthetically pleasing')">
                        <div class="suggestion-icon">🏗️</div>
                        <div class="suggestion-text">Engineering meets aesthetics</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="suggestion-card" onclick="sendSuggestion('How would Leonardo approach sustainable urban planning?')">
                        <div class="suggestion-icon">🌱</div>
                        <div class="suggestion-text">Sustainable innovation</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="suggestion-card" onclick="sendSuggestion('Apply golden ratio principles to user interface design')">
                        <div class="suggestion-icon">📐</div>
                        <div class="suggestion-text">Mathematical harmony in design</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Input Area -->
        <div class="input-area">
            <input 
                type="text" 
                class="input-field" 
                id="messageInput"
                placeholder="Ask Leonardo's digital mind..."
                onkeypress="handleKeyPress(event)"
            >
            <button class="btn-send" onclick="sendMessage()">
                <svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M2.01 21L23 12 2.01 3 2 10l15 2-15 2z"/>
                </svg>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        let conversationStarted = false;

        function handleKeyPress(event) {
            if (event.key === 'Enter' && !event.shiftKey) {
                event.preventDefault();
                sendMessage();
            }
        }

        function sendSuggestion(text) {
            document.getElementById('messageInput').value = text;
            sendMessage();
        }

        function sendMessage() {
            const input = document.getElementById('messageInput');
            const message = input.value.trim();
            
            if (message === '') return;
            
            const messagesArea = document.getElementById('messagesArea');
            
            // Hide welcome screen on first message
            if (!conversationStarted) {
                document.getElementById('welcomeScreen').style.display = 'none';
                conversationStarted = true;
            }
            
            // Add user message
            const userMessage = document.createElement('div');
            userMessage.className = 'message user';
            userMessage.innerHTML = `
                <div class="message-content">${message}</div>
            `;
            messagesArea.appendChild(userMessage);
            
            // Clear input
            input.value = '';
            
            // Show thinking indicator
            const thinkingMessage = document.createElement('div');
            thinkingMessage.className = 'message assistant';
            thinkingMessage.innerHTML = `
                <div class="message-meta">
                    <span>DVNC.ai</span>
                    <span>• Analyzing across domains</span>
                </div>
                <div class="thinking-indicator">
                    <div class="thinking-dot"></div>
                    <div class="thinking-dot"></div>
                    <div class="thinking-dot"></div>
                </div>
            `;
            messagesArea.appendChild(thinkingMessage);
            
            // Scroll to bottom
            messagesArea.scrollTop = messagesArea.scrollHeight;
            
            // Simulate response (in production, this would call your API)
            setTimeout(() => {
                thinkingMessage.remove();
                
                const assistantMessage = document.createElement('div');
                assistantMessage.className = 'message assistant';
                assistantMessage.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="message-meta">
                        <span>DVNC.ai</span>
                        <span>• Cross-domain synthesis complete</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="message-content">
                        ${generateLeonardoResponse(message)}
                    </div>
                `;
                messagesArea.appendChild(assistantMessage);
                messagesArea.scrollTop = messagesArea.scrollHeight;
            }, 2000);
        }

        function generateLeonardoResponse(query) {
            // This is a placeholder - in production, this would be your actual API response
            const responses = {
                'biomimicry': `Observing nature's cooling mechanisms, I see elegant solutions in termite mounds and elephant ears. 
                
The termite's passive ventilation system uses thermal gradients and strategic channel placement - principles we can apply to building design through computational fluid dynamics. Consider integrating bio-inspired heat exchangers with fractal geometries that maximize surface area while minimizing material use.

I envision a hybrid system combining the vascular networks of leaves with the phase-change properties of certain desert plants. This interdisciplinary approach merges biological observation with thermodynamic engineering.`,
                
                'bridge': `A bridge must be a dialogue between mathematical precision and visual poetry. 
                
Following the golden ratio (1.618...), we can create spans that please the eye while distributing forces optimally. Consider cable-stayed designs inspired by spider silk - nature's strongest material relative to weight. The main towers could echo Gothic cathedral proportions, marrying spiritual uplift with structural necessity.

Integration of parametric design tools with biomechanical stress patterns from bone structures could yield unprecedented strength-to-weight ratios.`,
                
                'urban': `Cities are living organisms requiring circulatory systems, nervous networks, and metabolic processes.
                
I propose neighborhoods as cells, with permeable boundaries allowing controlled exchange. Green corridors serve as arteries, carrying not just people but biodiversity. Buildings should breathe like lungs, with adaptive facades responding to environmental conditions.

Water management mimics watershed patterns, while energy distribution follows neural network principles for resilience and efficiency.`,
                
                'golden': `The golden ratio manifests in both natural forms and human perception of beauty.
                
For interface design, apply φ to establish hierarchies: primary content occupies 61.8% of space, secondary 38.2%. This creates visual balance that feels intuitively correct. Navigation elements can follow Fibonacci sequences (1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8...) for spacing and sizing.

Consider how the spiral of a nautilus shell might inform scrolling behaviors and information architecture.`,
                
                'default': `Your query opens fascinating interdisciplinary pathways.
                
Like my historical namesake, I approach this by first observing patterns across domains - what can fluid dynamics teach us about information flow? How might botanical growth patterns inform algorithmic design?

I see connections between seemingly disparate fields that could yield innovative solutions. Would you like me to explore specific aspects through the lenses of art, engineering, biology, or physics?`
            };
            
            // Simple keyword matching for demo
            for (let key in responses) {
                if (query.toLowerCase().includes(key)) {
                    return responses[key];
                }
            }
            
            return responses.default;
        }

        // Mode switching
        document.querySelectorAll('.mode-btn').forEach(btn => {
            btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                document.querySelectorAll('.mode-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
                this.classList.add('active');
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
